org.nevec.rjm

Class Wigner3jGUI

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.nevec.rjm.Wigner3jGUI
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ActionListener, EventListener, ListSelectionListener

    public class Wigner3jGUI
extends Object
implements ActionListener, ListSelectionListener
    An interactive interface to the Wigner3j class. The GUI allows to preselect one of the symbols if the number of j-terms is small (6j up to 15j), or to enter any other connectivity for the triads of j-values. The actual j-values are entered as integers (2j+1) and the computation of one value (in exact square root representation) is started manually.
    Since:
    2011-02-15
